# Puissance-4-cli (Game terminal)

# Introduction
Hello, new gamer! Now you are faced with the Quiz. You can play on diffrent theme and seris

# To install
Clone the repository "https://github.com/JessyPiTech/Quiz.git" and navigate to the Quiz folder using your terminal.

# To start, execute "make build" in the root directory. Then, do make run and start en game with an friend. 
After playing, press Ctrl+C and run "make clean".

Enjoy your game!
